    "Limitation 3: Maintaining critical thinking and creativityA significant issue is the diminishing capacity for critical analysis and inventive thought in students who become too reliant on AI tools [9,56].",
    "Education's core aim is to nurture curiosity, prompting learners to interrogate, dispute, and invent with language.",
